data.actual_result: I see a random partial list of the members and I cannot add the one I want if he's not in the list.
data.expected_result: I should see all the members in the server and choose the one I want to add.
data.short_description: Random partial members list when I try to add a member in a channel permission, on lazy guild.
data.steps_to_repro: - Open a lazy guild. - Enter in a channel. - Press on channel name (on top) to open its settings. - Select the Permissions tab. - Select Add a member.
